=== 神秘的魔法石（2001） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：神秘的魔法石 (電影)}}
[[File:_David_Heyman1.jpg|thumb]]製作了每一部魔法世界的電影。]]
一個看似普通11歲男孩的[[哈利·波特_(角色)|哈利·波特]]，實際上他是個[[巫師|巫師]]，也是[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]試圖崛起的倖存者。哈利被[[魯霸·海格|魯霸·海格]]從他不友善的[[麻瓜|麻瓜]]親戚—弗農姨丈、姨姨佩妮和他的表弟達力手中救出，並送到[[霍格華茲魔法與巫術學院|霍格華茲魔法學校]]就讀，哈利於那裡跟他的朋友[[榮恩·衛斯理|榮恩·衛斯理]]和[[妙麗·格蘭傑|妙麗·格蘭傑]]陷入了被保存在學校裡的[[魔法石|魔法石]]的謎團之中。

1998年10月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]在製片人[[大衛·海曼|大衛·海曼]]的推薦下<ref name="HeymanPitch">{{cite news|url=https://ew.com/article/2001/09/14/harry-potter-comes-alive/ |title=Harry Potter Comes Alive |date=2001-09-14 |last1=Jensen |first1=Jeff |last2=Fierman |first2=Daniel |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511143456/http://ew.com/article/2001/09/14/harry-potter-comes-alive/ |archive-date=2017-05-11 }}</ref> 
以七位數的價格購下了[[J·K·羅琳|J·K·羅琳]]的奇幻系列《[[哈利·波特|哈利波特]]》首四部小說的電影版權<ref name=" HeymanPitch" /><ref name="HPFilmRights">{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/books-cover-stories-at-the-frankfurt-book-fair-1177247.html |title=Books: Cover Stories At the Frankfurt Book Fair |date=1998-10-09 |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |access-date=2017-07-09 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170629172006/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/books-cover-stories-at-the-frankfurt-book-fair-1177247.html |archive-date=2017-06-29 }}</ref>，華納兄弟在草擬合同時特別注意到羅琳對這些電影的願望與想法。她的主要規定之一是他們在英國需以全體英國演員拍攝，這已被普遍遵守<ref name="BritishCast">{{Cite news|title=J.K. Rowling, the interview |url=http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/2000/0600-times-treneman.html |date=2000-06-30 |work=[[The_Times|The Times]] |last=Treneman |first=Ann |access-date=2017-07-07 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070203102312/http://www.accio-quote.org/articles/2000/0600-times-treneman.html |archive-date=2007-02-03 }}</ref>。2000年8月8日，籍籍無名的[[丹尼尔·拉德克利夫|丹尼爾·域卡夫]]與新演員[[魯伯特·葛林|魯拔·格連特]]和[[艾玛·沃森|愛瑪·屈臣]]分別被選中飾演[[哈利·波特_(角色)|哈利·波特]]、[[榮恩·衛斯理|榮恩·衛斯理]]及[[妙麗·格蘭傑|妙麗·格蘭傑]]。[[克里斯·哥倫布|基斯·哥倫布]]獲聘為改編電影《{{哈利波特1}}》執導，而[[史提夫·克羅夫斯|史提夫·克羅夫斯]]獲選編寫劇本<ref name="KlovesScreenplay">{{cite web|url=http://archive.salon.com/ent/col/srag/2000/02/24/kloves/index.html|title=A Wizard of Hollywood|last=Sragow|first=Michael|date=2000-02-24|access-date=2007-07-08|work=[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070710191745/http://archive.salon.com/ent/col/srag/2000/02/24/kloves/index.html|archive-date=2007-07-10}}</ref>。拍攝於2000年9月29日在[[華納兄弟利維斯登工作室|華納兄弟利維斯登工作室]]開始，並於2001年3月23日結束<ref name="HP1Filming">{{cite web|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/451961/Harry-Potter-and-the-Sorcerer-s-Stone/misc-notes.html |title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone misc notes |publisher=[[Turner_Classic_Movies|Turner Classic Movies]] |access-date=2015-10-21 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107155658/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/451961/Harry-Potter-and-the-Sorcerer-s-Stone/misc-notes.html |archive-date=2016-01-07 }}</ref><ref name="HPLeavesden">{{cite news|url=http://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/en/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden |title=Harry Potter at Leavesden |publisher=WB Studio Tour |access-date=2012-09-16 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225090955/http://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/en/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden |archive-date=2012-02-25  }}</ref>，最終工作於同年7月完成<ref name="HP1PostYahoo">{{cite web|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331|title=Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone (2001)|last=Schmitz|first=Greg Dean|publisher=[[Yahoo!_Movies|Yahoo! Movies]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215132239/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404331|archive-date=2007-12-15|access-date=2008-08-09}}</ref>。[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2000年10月2日在[[北約克郡|北約克郡]]的{{le|高斯蘭站|Goathland railway station}}進行<ref name="HP1PPhotography">{{cite web|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034123p1.html |title=Potter Pics: Hagrid, Hogsmeade Station, and the Hogwarts Express |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-10-02 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=2007-07-09 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831201714/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034123p1.html |archive-date=2011-08-31 }}</ref>。華納兄弟最初計劃在2001年7月4日那周末發行這部電影，然而由於製作時間如此之短，以致幾位獲提名的導演把自己排除在考慮之列外。由於時間上的限制，電影的上映日期被推遲，《{{哈利波特1}}》於2001年11月16日在英國和美國上映<ref name="HP1Release">{{cite web|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034103p1.html |title=Bewitched Warner Bros. Delays Potter |last=Linder |first=Brian |date=2000-05-17 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=2007-07-08 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206110507/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/034/034103p1.html |archive-date=2008-12-06 }}</ref>。

=== 消失的密室（2002） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：消失的密室 (電影)}}
哈利、榮恩和妙麗等人回到霍格華茲繼續他們的二年級的學業，但隱藏於學校裡的一個[[霍格華茲魔法學校#地底深處|消失的密室]]被打開，讓學生和鬼魂被一名身份不明的東西嚇呆了。三人必須解開密室之謎，並找到密室的入口，才能找到並擊敗真正的罪魁禍首。

哥倫布與克羅夫斯回歸劇組，分別擔任電影《{{哈利波特2}}》的導演和編劇<ref name="Columbus2" /><ref name="Kloves" />。在第一部電影廣泛發行僅三天之後，這部電影的製作於2001年11月19日在英國[[薩里郡|薩里郡]]開始，並在[[曼島|人島]]以及在英國的其他幾個地方繼續進行外景拍攝。倫敦的[[華納兄弟利維斯登工作室|華納兄弟利維斯登工作室]]為霍格華茲製作了幾個場景<ref name="HP2FilmingEnd">{{cite web|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/shop?d=hp&cf=prev&id=1808404332|title=''Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets'' – Greg's Preview. Yahoo! Movies|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070621034511/http://movies.yahoo.com/shop?d=hp&cf=prev&id=1808404332|archive-date=2007-06-21}}</ref><ref name="HP2Locations">{{cite web|url=http://www.gloucestershireonscreen.co.uk/home/2000s/harry-potter-and-the-chamber-of-secrets-2002|title=Harry Potter Filming Locations|work=Gloucestershire on Screen|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304125126/http://www.gloucestershireonscreen.co.uk/home/2000s/harry-potter-and-the-chamber-of-secrets-2002|archive-date=2012-03-04}}</ref>。主體拍攝於2002年夏天結束<ref name="HP2FilmingEnd" />。這部電影一直持續到10月初才進入[[後期製作|後期製作]]<ref name="HP2Post">{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2300000/2300629.stm |title=Potter film should be finished next week |date=2002-10-04 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2012-10-16 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313184752/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2300000/2300629.stm |archive-date=2014-03-13 }}</ref>。《{{哈利波特2}}》於2002年11月3日在英國首映，隨後於11月15日（即神秘的魔法石上映的一年後）廣泛上映<ref name="HP2PremiereUK">{{Cite web|url=https://www.warnerbros.com/studio/news/warner-bros-online-webcast-world-premiere-%E2%80%9Charry-potter-and-chamber-secrets%E2%80%9D-live-london|title=Warner Bros. Online To Webcast World Premiere Of "Harry Potter And The Chamber Of Secrets" Live From London|date=2002-10-31|publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]]|access-date=2017-07-06|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714173509/https://www.warnerbros.com/studio/news/warner-bros-online-webcast-world-premiere-%E2%80%9Charry-potter-and-chamber-secrets%E2%80%9D-live-london|archive-date=2017-07-14}}</ref> <ref name="HPTotalBOM">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=harrypotter.htm |title=Harry Potter Movies at the Box Office |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=2017-07-04 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630171841/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=harrypotter.htm |archive-date=2017-06-30 }}</ref>。

=== 阿茲卡班的逃犯（2004） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯 (電影)}}
一個神秘的罪犯[[天狼星·布萊克|天狼星·布萊克]]從[[哈利波特中的地點#阿兹卡班監獄|阿茲卡班監獄]]逃脫，並把其目光投向霍格華茲—[[哈利波特中的生物#催狂魔|催狂魔]]駐紮在那裡以保護哈利與他的同學。這讓哈利更了解自己的過去以及自己跟這個逃犯的關聯。

曾擔任首兩輯電影導演的哥倫布起初決定不再回歸執掌第三輯電影<ref name="Columbus2" />，但他仍會跟海曼一起擔任製片人<ref name="CuaronConnection">{{cite news|url=http://www.scifi.com/sfw/issue372/interview.html|title=The creators of Harry Potter break out of character to discuss The Prisoner of Azkaban|last=Dickey|first=Lucinda|work=Science Fiction Weekly|access-date=2007-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040615094904/http://www.scifi.com/sfw/issue372/interview.html|archive-date=2004-06-15}}</ref>。華納兄弟隨後為哥倫布的接任人擬定了一份三人的短名單，其中包括{{le|卡莉·克里|Callie Khouri}}、[[簡尼夫·班納|簡尼夫·班納]]（在《消失的密室》中飾演[[霍格華茲教職員#吉德羅·洛哈|吉德羅·洛哈]]），以及最終成為該電影導演的[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]<ref name="Cuaron" />。柯朗最初對接受這份工作感到緊張，因為他沒有閱讀過任何小說，也沒有看過該系列的電影，但後來在閱讀了該系列的小說就能立即把故事串連聯繫起來後便簽約<ref name="CuaronConnection" /><ref name="CuaronNervous">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_3758000/3758101.stm |title=Alfonso Cuaron: the man behind the magic |date=2004-05-24 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2007-10-10 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071107164356/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_3758000/3758101.stm |archive-date=2007-11-07 }}</ref>。在首兩輯電影中飾演[[阿不思·鄧不利多|阿不思·鄧不利多]]的[[李察·哈里斯|李察·哈里斯]]，由於他於2002年10月去世<ref name="HarrisDeath">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/2362935.stm |title=Actor Richard Harris dies |date=2002-10-25 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |access-date=2007-10-10 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20021206102152/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/film/2362935.stm |archive-date=2002-12-06 }}</ref>，因此其角色由[[邁可·坎邦|米高·甘邦]]接替<ref name="Gambon" /><ref name="HarrisDeath" />。甘邦並不關心改善或複製哈里斯，而是給出了他自己的演譯，包括在角色中使用輕微的愛爾蘭口音<ref name="HP3castinterviews">{{cite video|year=2004|title=Head to Shrunken Head|medium=DVD|people=[[Johnny_Vaughan|Vaughan, Johnny]]; [[Lenny_Henry|Henry, Lenny]]|publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]]}}</ref>，他在三周內完成了他的場景<ref name="GambonFilming">{{cite news|url=http://news.scotsman.com/topics.cfm?tid=3&id=613682004|title=Olivier, Dumbledore and two broken ribs|last=Synnot|first=Siobhan|date=2004-05-30|work=[[The_Scotsman|The Scotsman]]|access-date=2007-11-30 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070525052700/http://news.scotsman.com/topics.cfm?tid=3&id=613682004 |archive-date=2007-05-25 }}</ref>。[[加里·奧德曼|加利·奧文]]於2003年2月獲選為飾演關鍵角色天狼星·布萊克<ref name="HP3FilmingBegin"/>。主體拍攝在2003年2月24日於利維斯登電影製片廠開始<ref name="HP3FilmingBegin">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2788000/2788225.stm |title=Dumbledore and Sirius cast for Azkaban |date=2003-02-21 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2007-10-10 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070808165333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/tv_film/newsid_2788000/2788225.stm |archive-date=2007-08-08 }}</ref>，並於2003年10月結束<ref name="HP3FilmingEnd">{{cite web|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404333 |title=Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (2004) |last=Schmitz |first=Greg Dean |publisher=[[Yahoo!_Movies|Yahoo! Movies]] |access-date=2007-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070716011517/https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/preview/1808404333 |archive-date=2007-07-16 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。《{{哈利波特3}}》於2004年5月23日在紐約首映<ref name="HP3Premiere">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3741103.stm |title=Potter star mobbed at US premiere |date=2004-05-24 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |access-date=2012-10-17 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008230515/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/3741103.stm |archive-date=2013-10-08 }}</ref>，它於5月31日在英國上映，6月4日在美國上映<ref name="HP3Release" />。這是該系列中首部同時在傳統與[[IMAX|IMAX]]影院上映的電影<ref name="HP3IMAX">{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_3333000/3333477.stm |title=Potter 3 will be screened on IMAX |date=2003-12-19 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2012-10-17 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403051028/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_3333000/3333477.stm |archive-date=2015-04-03 }}</ref>。

=== 火盃的考驗（2005） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：火盃的考驗 (電影)}}
[[魁地奇|魁地奇]]世界盃結束後，哈利回到霍格華茲並發現自己參加了[[哈利·波特与火焰杯|三巫鬥法大賽]]，那是一項涉及完成三項具挑戰性危險任務的比賽。哈利被迫跟火盃選擇的另外三名巫師進行競賽—[[花兒·戴樂古|花兒·戴樂古]]、維克多·喀浪和[[西追·迪哥里|西追·迪哥里]]。

2003年8月，在《阿茲卡班的逃犯》的導演[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]宣布不會執導續集之後，英國電影導演[[米克·紐維爾|米克·紐維爾]]獲選為電影執導。海曼回歸製作人的崗位，而克羅夫斯再次為該系列電影編寫劇本<ref name="Newell" />。主體拍攝於2004年5月4日展開<ref name="HP4PPhotography">{{cite web|url=http://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/en/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden|title=Harry Potter at Leavesden|year=2011|publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]]|access-date=2012-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726094544/https://www.wbstudiotour.co.uk/about-us/harry-potter-at-leavesden|archive-date=2014-07-26}}</ref>，涉及電影主要演員的場景於2004年6月25日在英國的利維斯登電影製片廠開始拍攝<ref name="HP4FilmingBegin">{{cite web|url=http://people.com/celebrity/ralph-fiennes-ready-to-scare-harry-potter/|title=Ralph Fiennes Ready to Scare Harry Potter|last=Silverman|first=Stephen|date=2004-08-05|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|access-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714173509/http://people.com/celebrity/ralph-fiennes-ready-to-scare-harry-potter/|archive-date=2017-07-14}}</ref><ref name="HP4Production">{{cite web |url=http://movies.about.com/od/harrypotter4/a/goblet062904.htm |title="Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire" Production News |date=2004-06-25 |publisher=[[About.com|About.com]] |last=Murray |first=Rebecca |access-date=2012-10-12 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050922133337/http://movies.about.com/od/harrypotter4/a/goblet062904.htm |archive-date=2005-09-22 }}</ref>。《哈利波特：火盃的考驗》於2005年11月6日在倫敦舉行首映<ref name="HP4Premiere">{{cite news|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-11-06-potter-premiere_x.htm|title='Harry Potter' cast attends London premiere|date=2005-11-06|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050922133337/http://movies.about.com/od/harrypotter4/a/goblet062904.htm |archive-date=2005-09-22 }}</ref>，並於11月18日在英國和美國上映<ref name="HP4Release">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4509435.stm |title=Potter film to get Imax release |date=2005-05-03 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711141531/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2005-11-06-potter-premiere_x.htm |archive-date=2017-07-11 }}</ref>。《火盃的考驗》是該系列中第一部獲得[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]（MPAA）的[[美國電影分級制度#美國電影協會電影分級|PG-13]]的評級，原因是「幻想暴力和令人恐懼的畫面」<ref name="HP4ratingMPAA">{{Cite news|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/506503-potter_grows_up_and_goblet_of_fire_is_pg_13|title=Potter Grows Up and 'Goblet of Fire' is PG-13|date=2005-08-09|publisher=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]]|access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714173509/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/506503-potter_grows_up_and_goblet_of_fire_is_pg_13 |archive-date=2017-07-14 }}</ref>；[[澳大利亞分級委員會|澳大利亞分級委員會]]（ACB）給予M的級別<ref name="HP4ratingACB">{{Cite web|url=http://raisingchildren.net.au/movies/harry_potter_and_the_goblet_of_fire_movie.html |title=Harry Potter (4) and the Goblet of Fire |publisher=[[Raising_Children_Network|Raising Children Network]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221113144/http://raisingchildren.net.au/movies/harry_potter_and_the_goblet_of_fire_movie.html |archive-date=2016-02-21 }}</ref>；[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]（BBFC）就著其黑暗主題、幻想暴力、威脅和令人恐懼的圖像而給予12A的評級<ref name="HP4ratingBBFC">{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4350000/newsid_4358300/4358388.stm |title=How Goblet of Fire got its 12A rating |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |date=2005-10-19 |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160416224514/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4350000/newsid_4358300/4358388.stm |archive-date=2016-04-16 }}</ref>。

=== 鳳凰會的密令（2007） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令 (電影)}}
