哈利回到霍格華茲繼續其第五年的學業，並發現[[哈利波特世界觀與設定|魔法世界]]否認[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]捲土重來的事實。他把事情掌握於自己手中並成立了一個秘密組織來對抗霍格華茲「高級調查官」[[桃樂絲·恩不里居|桃樂絲·恩不里居]]的政權，以及為即將到來的戰鬥學習實用性的[[哈利波特中的魔法符咒#黑魔法防禦術|黑魔法防禦術]]<ref name=PhoenixSynopsis>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/10/05/official-harry-potter-and-the-order-of-the-phoenix-logo/|title=Official 'Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix' Logo|publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]]|date=2006-10-05|access-date=2017-07-06|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201085811/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/10/05/official-harry-potter-and-the-order-of-the-phoenix-logo/}}</ref>。

[[丹尼爾·域卡夫|丹尼爾·域卡夫]]確認他將於2005年5月以[[哈利·波特_(角色)|哈利·波特]]的身分回歸劇組<ref name="HP5Radcliffe">{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-05-03-potter-sidebar_x.htm|title=There's no looking back|last=Puig|first=Claudia|date=2005-05-03|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629105527/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2005-05-03-potter-sidebar_x.htm |archive-date=2011-06-29 }}</ref>，而[[魯伯特·葛林|魯拔·格連特]]、[[艾玛·沃森|愛瑪·屈臣]]、[[馬修·路易斯|馬修·路易斯]]（[[纳威·隆巴顿|奈威·隆巴頓]]）及[[邦妮·赖特|邦妮·韋特]]（[[金妮·衛斯理|金妮·衛斯理]]）確認於2005年11月回歸劇組<ref name="HP5Grint">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4440000/newsid_4443900/4443956.stm |title=NR chats to GOF's Rupert Grint |date=2005-11-16 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606075239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4440000/newsid_4443900/4443956.stm |archive-date=2017-06-06 }}</ref><ref name="HP5Watson">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4440000/newsid_4443700/4443762.stm |title=NR chats to GOF's Emma Watson |date=2005-11-16 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919101355/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4440000/newsid_4443700/4443762.stm |archive-date=2016-09-19 }}</ref><ref name="HP5Lewis">{{cite news|url=http://www.mugglenet.com/chat/transcripts/mattlewis250805.htm|title=Matthew Lewis: Online Q&A session|date=2005-08-25|publisher=[[MuggleNet|MuggleNet]]|access-date=2006-10-23|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061108155847/http://www.mugglenet.com/chat/transcripts/mattlewis250805.htm|archive-date=2006-11-08}}</ref><ref name="HP5Wright">{{cite news|url=http://teacher.scholastic.com/scholasticnews/indepth/harry_potter_movie_iv/interviews/index.asp?article=wright|title=Bonnie Wright as Ginny Weasley in ''Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire''|last1=Linn|first1=Laura|last2=Morreale|first2=Marie|date=2005-11-26|work=[[Scholastic_Corporation|Scholastic News]]|access-date=2017-07-06|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710153035/http://teacher.scholastic.com/scholasticnews/indepth/harry_potter_movie_iv/interviews/index.asp?article=wright|archive-date=2017-07-10}}</ref>。2006年2月，[[海伦·麦克洛瑞|海倫·麥歌莉]]被選為飾演[[貝拉·雷斯壯|貝拉·雷斯壯]]<ref name="McCrory">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4670000/newsid_4672700/4672798.stm |title=Luna Lovegood role has been cast |date=2006-02-02 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208221115/http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/newsid_4670000/newsid_4672700/4672798.stm |archive-date=2017-02-08 }}</ref>，但她由於懷孕而辭演，[[海倫娜·寶咸·卡達|海倫娜·寶咸·卡達]]於2006年5月補上其位置<ref name="BonhamCarter" />。[[雷夫·范恩斯|賴夫·費恩斯]]再次擔任飾演佛地魔 (Lord Voldemort) 的角色<ref name="HP5Fiennes">{{cite news|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/news/topnews.php?id=10724|title=Ralph Fiennes on Lord Voldemort|date=2005-08-09|publisher=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]]|access-date=2006-10-23|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061018212527/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/topnews.php?id=10724|archive-date=2006-10-18}}</ref>。繼《火盃的考驗》的導演[[米克·紐維爾|米克·紐維爾]]，以及[[尚-彼亞·桑里|尚-彼亞·桑里]]、[[哥連慕·迪多奴|哥連慕·迪多奴]]、[[馬菲·域肯|馬菲·域肯]]及[[米拉·奈兒|米拉·奈兒]]拒絕為電影執導後，英國電視導演[[大衛·葉慈|大衛·葉慈]]獲選為電影導演<ref name="HP5Director">{{cite news|url=https://ew.com/article/2007/07/13/set-secrets-darkest-harry-movie-yet/ |title=On-set secrets from the darkest ''Harry'' movie yet |last=Daly |first=Steve |date=2007-07-13 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027151235/http://www.ew.com/article/2007/07/13/set-secrets-darkest-harry-movie-yet |archive-date=2016-10-27 }}</ref><ref name="HP5Director2">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jun/24/harrypotter |title=How I raised Potter's bar |last=Raphael |first=Amy |date=2007-06-24 |work=[[The_Observer|The Observer]] |location=London |access-date=2007-06-26 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225033001/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jun/24/harrypotter |archive-date=2013-12-25 }}</ref>。首四輯《哈利波特》電影編劇的克羅夫斯，由於他還有其他承諾，而曾經獲考慮擔任該系列第一部電影編劇的{{le|米高·戈登伯格|Michael Goldenberg}}則補上填寫劇本<ref name="Goldenberg" />。主體拍攝於2006年2月7日展開，並於2006年12月上旬結束<ref name="HP5FilmingBegin">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/1/27/em-order-of-the-phoenix-em-movie-rehearsals-starting |title=Order of the Phoenix Movie Rehearsals Starting |date=2006-01-27 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2006-12-30 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070724195416/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/1/27/em-order-of-the-phoenix-em-movie-rehearsals-starting |archive-date=2007-07-24 }}</ref> <ref name="HP5TLC">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/12/29/2006-the-year-in-em-harry-potter-em-film |title=2006: The Year in Harry Potter Film |date=2006-12-29 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2006-12-30 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927002431/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/12/29/2006-the-year-in-em-harry-potter-em-film |archive-date=2007-09-27 }}</ref>。拍攝從2006年5月開始，期間暫停了兩個月，好讓域卡夫能夠參與其[[普通教育高级程度证书|普通教育高級程度證書]]（A-Level考試），而屈臣也可以應考其[[中等教育普通證書|中等教育普通證書]]（GCSE考試）<ref name="HP5FilmingHiatus">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/exclusive-order-phoenix-news/ |title=Exclusive: Order of the Phoenix News |date=14 March 2006 |magazine=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |access-date=2 August 2007 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107162936/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/exclusive-order-phoenix-news/ |archive-date=7 January 2016 }}</ref>。實景拍攝在英格蘭和蘇格蘭進行外景拍攝，並在利維斯登電影製片廠進行室內外景拍攝<ref name="HP5Locations">{{cite news|url=http://www.mugglenet.com/newsfusion/fullnews.php?id=752|title=Yates comments on OOTP hold-up|date=2005-05-27|publisher=[[MuggleNet|MuggleNet]]|access-date=2006-10-23|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102222427/http://www.mugglenet.com/newsfusion/fullnews.php?id=752|archive-date=2007-11-02}}</ref><ref name="HP5Locations2">{{cite news|url=http://summermovies.fandango.com/roadtriparticle.php?ar_id=13|title=Harry Potter's Britain|last=Kern|first=Chris|publisher=[[Fandango_(company)|Fandango]]|access-date=2007-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703114702/http://summermovies.fandango.com/roadtriparticle.php?ar_id=13|archive-date=2007-07-03}}</ref><ref name="HP5Locations3">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/7/4/new-privet-drive-set-photos-from-ootp |title=New Privet Drive Set Photos from OotP |date=2006-07-04 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2007-02-24 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070724193234/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2006/7/4/new-privet-drive-set-photos-from-ootp |archive-date=2007-07-24 }}</ref>。《[[哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令_(電影)|哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令]]》於2007年6月28日在日本東京舉行了全球首映<ref name="HP5TokyoPremiere">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/6679263.stm |title=Japanese debut for Potter movie |date=2007-05-22 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070713014329/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/6679263.stm |archive-date=2007-07-13 }}</ref>，並於7月3日在英國倫敦[[萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院|萊斯特廣場奧迪安電影院]]進行了英國首映<ref name="HP5UKPremiere">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6266590.stm |title=Fans brave rain for Potter stars |date=2007-07-03 |work=[[Newsround|CBBC Newsround]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702055000/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6266590.stm |archive-date=2016-07-02 }}</ref>。電影於7月11日在美國上映<ref name="HP5USRelease">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/05/29/confirmed-change-to-us-order-of-the-phoenix-release-date-now-july-11/ |title=Confirmed: Change to US "Order of the Phoenix" Release Date, Now 11 July |date=2007-05-29 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160614182132/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/05/29/confirmed-change-to-us-order-of-the-phoenix-release-date-now-july-11/ |archive-date=2016-06-14 }}</ref>，而7月12日於英國上映<ref name="HP5UKRelease">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/5/11/change-to-uk-ootp-date-now-july-12 |title=Change to UK "OotP" Date: Now 12 July |date=2007-05-11 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306205426/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/5/11/change-to-uk-ootp-date-now-july-12/ |archive-date=2016-03-06 }}</ref>。

=== 混血王子的背叛（2009） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛 (電影)}}
佛地魔和其食死人正在增加他們對巫師與麻瓜世界的恐懼。[[鄧不利多|鄧不利多]]校長出於重要原因需要幫助，他說服其老朋友[[霍格華茲教職員#赫瑞司·史拉轟|赫瑞司·史拉轟]]回到其於霍格華茲先前的職位。在史拉轟的魔藥課堂上，哈利得到了一本帶有奇怪註釋的教科書，這課本之前為「混血王子」所有<ref name="HBPSynopsis">{{cite web|url=http://hpana.com/news/20321 |title=Description & first official picture from 'Half-Blood Prince' |publisher=[[HPANA|HPANA]] |date=2017-12-14 |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324132125/http://hpana.com/news/20321 |archive-date=2016-03-24 }}</ref>。

2007年7月，電影公司宣布[[大衛·葉慈|大衛·葉慈]]將作為導演回歸<ref name="Yates2" />。在跳過第五部電影後，克羅夫斯重返編劇的崗位，而海曼和{{le|大衛·巴隆|David Barron (film producer)}}重新擔任製片人<ref name="HBPCast" />。愛瑪·屈臣曾經考慮不回來拍這部電影<ref name="HBPWatson">{{cite web|url=https://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/09/26/hermione-gets-cold-feet |title=Hermione Gets Cold Feet |author=Stax |date=2006-09-26 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319174520/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/09/26/hermione-gets-cold-feet |archive-date=2016-03-19 }}</ref>，但最終在華納兄弟公司調整了製作時間表以遷就其考試日期後便簽約<ref name="HBPWatsonEducation">{{Cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1652387/emma-watson-recalls-nearly-quitting-harry-potter/ |title=Emma Watson Recalls Nearly Quitting 'Harry Potter' |last=Ditzian |first=Eric |date=2010-11-16 |publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222015803/http://www.mtv.com/news/1652387/emma-watson-recalls-nearly-quitting-harry-potter/ |archive-date=2017-02-22 }}</ref>。主體拍攝於2007年9月24日開始<ref name="HBPFilmingBegin">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/9/19/half-blood-prince-filming-news-threat-of-strike-to-affect-harry-potter-six |title="Half-Blood Prince" Filming News: Threat of Strike to Affect Harry Potter Six? |date=2007-09-19 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323024456/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/9/19/half-blood-prince-filming-news-threat-of-strike-to-affect-harry-potter-six/ |archive-date=2016-03-23 }}</ref>，並於2008年5月17日結束<ref name="HBPFilmingEnd">{{Cite web|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2008/5/22/principle-photography-on-half-blood-prince-completed/ |title=Filming for "Half-Blood Prince" Completed |date=2008-05-22 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007193559/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2008/5/22/principle-photography-on-half-blood-prince-completed/ |archive-date=2016-10-07 }}</ref>。儘管域卡夫、甘邦和[[吉姆·布勞德本特|占·布勞德本特]]（史拉轟）於2007年9月下旬開始拍攝，然而其他演員的拍攝時間要晚得多：屈臣直到2007年12月才開始；[[阿倫·烈卡文|阿倫·烈卡文]]（[[賽佛勒斯·石內卜|賽佛勒斯·石內卜]]）直到2008年1月才開始；而卡特直到2008年2月<ref name="HBPFilmingWatsonRickman">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/11/28/half-blood-prince-filming-updates-with-emma-watson-alan-rickman-news |title="Half-Blood Prince" Filming Updates with Emma Watson, Alan Rickman News |date=2007-11-28 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2008-01-27 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319182544/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2007/11/28/half-blood-prince-filming-updates-with-emma-watson-alan-rickman-news |archive-date=2016-03-19 }}</ref><ref name="HBPFilmingBonhamCarter">{{cite news|url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3786&Itemid=99|title=Interviews: Depp, Burton, Carter and Rickman Slash Through Sweeney Todd!|last=Duke|first=Andy|date=2007-11-26|author2=Stephanie Sanchez|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209022646/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3786&Itemid=99|archive-date=2008-02-09|access-date=2008-01-27}}</ref>。《[[哈利波特：混血王子的背叛_(電影)|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛]]》於2009年7月6日在日本東京全球首映<ref name="HBPTokyoPremiere">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-40838420090706|title=Tokyo premiere launches return of 'Harry Potter'|last=Otagaki|first=Yumi|date=2009-07-06|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|access-date=2017-07-07 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714150303/http://www.reuters.com/article/idINIndia-40838420090706 |archive-date=2017-07-14 }}</ref>，並於7月15日在英國和美國上映<ref name="HBPWorldRelease">{{cite news|url=http://harrypotter.warnerbros.co.uk/releasedates/ |title=Official Release Dates |publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100103115555/http://harrypotter.warnerbros.co.uk/releasedates/ |archive-date=2010-01-03 |access-date=2010-11-07 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。

=== 死神的聖物Ⅰ（2010） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅰ}}
哈利、榮恩和妙麗離開了霍格華茲，並踏上尋找並摧毀佛地魔永生的秘密——[[哈利波特中的魔法物品#分靈體|分靈體]]之旅。這三人組經歷了漫長的旅程，他們在路途上遇到了許多障礙，包括食死人、掠奪者、神秘的死神聖物，以及哈利與黑魔王思想的連接變得越來越強<ref name="DH1Synopsis">{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=67254 |title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Trailer Online Monday |publisher=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]] |date=2010-06-23 |access-date=2017-07-05 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100626094437/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=67254 |archive-date=2010-06-26 }}</ref>。

電影原訂於2008年3月13日在單一院線上映，華納兄弟公司宣布為了公平對待小說以及出於對其粉絲的尊重，《[[哈利波特－死神的聖物|哈利波特－死神的聖物]]》的電影將會分為兩部分推出<ref name="DHTwoPart">{{cite press release|url=http://www.businesswire.com/portal/site/google/?ndmViewId=news_view&newsId=20080313005332&newsLang=en|title=Warner Bros. Plans Two-Part Film Adaptation of "Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows" to Be Directed by David Yates|date=13 March 2008|publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]]|agency=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]]|quote=...expand the screen adaptation of Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows and release the film in two parts.|access-date=6 September 2012 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628180059/http://www.businesswire.com/portal/site/google/?ndmViewId=news_view&newsId=20080313005332&newsLang=en |archive-date=28 June 2017 }}</ref>。前兩部電影的導演[[大衛·葉慈|大衛·葉慈]]確認回歸導演的崗位，而克羅夫斯確認擔任編劇<ref name="DHTwoPart" />。在該系列中，羅琳首次跟海曼和巴倫一起作為製作人，然而葉慈指出，她對電影製作過程的參與跟之前的電影相比並沒有改變<ref name="DHRowlingProducer">{{cite news|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/322593/david-yates-discusses-harry-potter-and-deathly-hallows-part-2 |title=David Yates discusses 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2' |date=2011-06-14 |work=Manila Bulletin Publishing Corporation |access-date=2011-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120910200917/http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/322593/david-yates-discusses-harry-potter-and-deathly-hallows-part-2 |archive-date=2012-09-10 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name="DHProducers">{{cite press release|title=Warner Bros. Pictures Worldwide Satellite Trailer Debut: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 1 |date=22 September 2010 |publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]] |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry |agency=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]] |quote=produced by David Heyman, David Barron and J.K. Rowling |access-date=9 February 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227092506/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100920005538/en/Warner-Bros.-Pictures-Worldwide-Satellite-Trailer-Debut%C2%A0Harry |archive-date=27 December 2010 }}</ref>。電影的前期製作於2009年1月26日開始<ref name="DHPreProd">{{cite news|url=http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2120 |title=Emma reveals DH test shooting begins this Monday |date=2009-01-20 |publisher=[[MuggleNet|MuggleNet]] |access-date=2009-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413233747/http://mugglenet.com/app/news/full_story/2120 |archive-date=2010-04-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref>，而[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]則於2月19日在利維斯登工作室開始，該系列的首六部作品都是在那裡拍攝的<ref name="HPLeavesden" />。{{le|松林工作室|Pinewood Studios}}成為了拍攝第七部電影的第二個工作室<ref name="DHLeavesdenPinewood">{{cite news|url=http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/25/harry-potter-movies-being-filmed-at-leavesden-and-pinewood-studios |title=Harry Potter Movies Being Filmed at Leavesden and Pinewood Studios |date=2009-03-25 |publisher=[[The_Leaky_Cauldron_(website)|The Leaky Cauldron]] |access-date=2009-03-26 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328221141/http://www.the-leaky-cauldron.org/2009/3/25/harry-potter-movies-being-filmed-at-leavesden-and-pinewood-studios |archive-date=2009-03-28 }}</ref>。
