=== 死神的聖物Ⅱ（2011） ===
{{Main|哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ}}

當哈利準備跟佛地魔的最後一戰時，哈利、榮恩和妙麗同時繼續尋找並摧毀餘下的分靈體<ref name="DH2Synopsis">{{cite web|url=http://www.hbo.com/movies/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-/synopsis.html |title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows (Part 2): Synopsis |publisher=[[HBO|HBO]] |access-date=2017-07-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103140214/http://www.hbo.com/movies/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-/synopsis.html |archive-date=2017-01-03 }}</ref>。這部電影於2008年3月獲宣佈作為[[哈利波特：死神的聖物製作過程|分拆電影的第二部分]]—《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利波特－死神的聖物Ⅱ]]》，當時據透露大衛·葉慈將為這部電影執導，而克洛夫斯將擔任編劇<ref name="DHTwoPart" />。2009年4月，在完成第一部分的劇本後，克洛夫斯開始著手編寫第二部分的劇本<ref name="DHKlovesScript">{{cite journal|date=April 2009|title=Hallowed Ground|journal=[[Empire_(film_magazine)|Empire]]|pages=100–104|author=Helen O'Hara}}</ref>。《死神的聖物Ⅱ》是在2009年2月19日至2010年6月12日期間跟《死神的聖物Ⅰ》以[[背靠背電影製作|背靠背電影製作]]方式拍攝<ref name="DHfilming">{{cite news|title=Longer spell at box office for Harry Potter|last=Malvern|first=Jack|date=2008-03-14|work=[[The_Times|The Times]]|location=UK}}</ref><ref name="HPLeavesden" /><ref name="DH2wraps">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1641491/harry-potter-filming-wraps-last-time.jhtml |title='Harry Potter' Filming Wraps – For The Last Time |last=Schwartz |first=Terri |date=2010-06-14 |publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |access-date=2012-12-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926011742/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1641491/harry-potter-filming-wraps-last-time.jhtml |archive-date=2011-09-26 }}</ref>，並於主體拍攝期間將其視作一部電影<ref name="DHoneFilm">{{cite news|url=https://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |title=Potter Producer Talks Deathly Hallows |last=Richards |first=Olly |date=2008-03-14 |work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |access-date=2008-03-14 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710192807/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |archive-date=2011-07-10 }}</ref>。原定於[[倫敦國王十字車站|倫敦國王十字車站]]進行的電影最終和尾聲場景的重新拍攝已確認將於2010年冬季開始，拍攝於2010年12月21日在利維斯登電影製片廠進行<ref name="DHreshoots">{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2010/12/22/harry-potter-reshoots-underway |title=Harry Potter Reshoots Underway |last=Goldman |first=Eric |date=2012-12-21 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |access-date=2012-12-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922021942/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/12/22/harry-potter-reshoots-underway |archive-date=2012-09-22 }}</ref>，標誌著歷時十年拍攝的《哈利波特》系列畫上了句號<ref name="HPwraps">{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/articles/daniel-radcliffe-and-emma-watson-confirm-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-pt-2-ending-reshoots |title=Daniel Radcliffe and Emma Watson confirm 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows, Pt 2' ending reshoots |last=Ellwood |first=Gregory |date=2010-11-11 |publisher=[[Hitfix|Hitfix]] |access-date=2017-07-07 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326104416/http://www.hitfix.com/articles/daniel-radcliffe-and-emma-watson-confirm-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-pt-2-ending-reshoots |archive-date=2016-03-26 }}</ref>。

這部電影於2011年7月7日在倫敦[[特拉法加廣場|特拉法加廣場]]舉行了全球首映禮<ref name="DH2UKPremiereRelease">{{cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/world-premiere-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-set-for-july-7/ |title=World premiere for ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2'' set for July 7 |last=SchwartPhillips |first=jevon |date=2011-03-01 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=2011-03-02 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025054232/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/world-premiere-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-set-for-july-7/ |archive-date=2013-10-25 }}</ref>，並於7月11日在紐約市[[林肯表演藝術中心|林肯表演藝術中心]]進行了美國首映<ref name="DH2USPremiere">{{cite web|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-premieres-in-new-york/ |title="Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2" premieres in New York |last=Derschowitz |first=Jessica |date=2011-07-12 |publisher=[[CBS_News|CBS News]] |access-date=2012-12-06 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928122450/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-premieres-in-new-york/ |archive-date=2015-09-28 }}</ref>。雖然電影是以2D拍攝，但在後期製作中轉為[[3D電影|3D電影]]，並在[[RealD_戲院|RealD 戲院]]和 IMAX 3D影院發行<ref name="DH2Imax3D">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/harry-potter-film-bow-record-210854 |title='Harry Potter' Film To Bow On Record 423 Global Imax Screens |last=Vlessing |first=Etan |date=2011-07-13 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2012-11-03 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913212053/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/harry-potter-film-bow-record-210854 |archive-date=2011-09-13 }}</ref>，成為該系列中首部以這種格式發行的電影<ref name="DH2_3D">{{cite web|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Harry-Potter-Fans-Choosing-2D-Over-3D-For-Deathly-Hallows-2-25307.html |title=Harry Potter Fans Choosing 2D Over 3D For Deathly Hallows 2 |publisher=Cinema Blend |last=Tyler |first=Josh |date=2012-05-29 |access-date=2017-07-07 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513181922/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Harry-Potter-Fans-Choosing-2D-Over-3D-For-Deathly-Hallows-2-25307.html |archive-date=2016-05-13 }}</ref>。這部電影於7月15日在英國和美國上映<ref name="DH2UKPremiereRelease">{{cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/world-premiere-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-set-for-july-7/ |title=World premiere for ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2'' set for July 7 |last=SchwartPhillips |first=jevon |date=2011-03-01 |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |access-date=2011-03-02 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025054232/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/world-premiere-for-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-set-for-july-7/ |archive-date=2013-10-25 }}</ref>。

