=== 怪獸與牠們的產地（2016） ===
{{Main|怪獸與牠們的產地 (電影)}}
[[File:J._K._Rowling_2010.jpg|thumb]]
故事講述1926年，[[紐特·斯卡曼德|紐特·斯卡曼德]]帶著其魔法行李箱抵達紐約市，該行李箱裡面載有許多危險的魔法生物及牠們的棲息地。有些魔法生物意外從其行李箱中逃了出來，紐特必須努力糾正這個錯誤，以及處理由此產生的暴力、恐懼，以及魔法和非魔法人類（[[麻瓜|麻瓜]]）之間的緊張局勢所帶來的恐怖<ref name="FBSynopsis">{{Cite news|url=https://ew.com/article/2015/11/04/fantastic-beasts/ |title='Fantastic Beasts' plot unveiled: Here's what the movie's about |last=Hibberd |first=James |date=2015-11-04 |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |access-date=2017-07-05 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217103217/http://ew.com/article/2015/11/04/fantastic-beasts/ |archive-date=2017-02-17 }}</ref>。

2013年9月12日，華納兄弟宣布羅琳正在根據她的小說《[[怪獸與牠們的產地|怪獸與牠們的產地]]》及當中虛構作者紐特·斯卡曼德的冒險經歷編寫成為劇本，該故事背景設定於《哈利波特》冒險故事的70年前。這部電影將標誌著她的編劇處女作，並計劃作為新系列的首部電影<ref name="FBScriptBook">{{cite web|title=Warner Bros. Announces Expanded Creative Partnership with J.K. Rowling |date=2013-09-12 |publisher=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]] |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20130912005870/en/Warner-Bros.-Announces-Expanded-Creative-Partnership-J.K. |access-date=2013-09-12 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130915102308/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20130912005870/en/Warner-Bros.-Announces-Expanded-Creative-Partnership-J.K. |archive-date=2013-09-15 }}</ref>。根據羅琳所說，在華納兄弟建議把故事改編後，她在12天內把劇本的草稿寫了出來。她說：「這不是一個很好的草稿，但它確實展示了其可能看起來的外觀。所以這就是一切的開始<ref name="FBDraft">{{cite web|title=J.K. Rowling wrote the 'Fantastic Beasts' rough draft in twelve days, wants to be an extra in drag |publisher=Hypable |url=http://www.hypable.com/2014/02/07/fantastic-beasts-movie-jk-rowling-emma-watson-interview/ |date=2014-02-07 |access-date=2014-02-08 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140208035531/http://www.hypable.com/2014/02/07/fantastic-beasts-movie-jk-rowling-emma-watson-interview/ |archive-date=2014-02-08 }}</ref>。」2014年3月，據透露預定三部曲的第一部設定於紐約<ref name="FBTrilogy">{{cite news|title=Warner's C.E.O. Is Bullish on the Big Screen |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/business/media/warners-ceo-is-bullish-on-the-big-screen.html |date=2014-03-29 |access-date=2014-03-29 |first=Brooks |last=Barnes |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329221855/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/business/media/warners-ceo-is-bullish-on-the-big-screen.html |archive-date=2014-03-29 }}</ref>，這部電影也見證了製片人大衛·海曼和編劇史蒂夫·克洛夫斯的回歸，他們都是《哈利波特》系列電影的老手<ref name="FBHeyman">{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2013/10/02/harry-potter-fantastic-beasts-david-heyman/ |title='Harry Potter' producer David Heyman talks 'Fantastic Beasts' spinoff |last=Smith |first=Grady |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2013-10-02 |access-date=2018-06-18 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618143430/http://www.ew.com/article/2013/10/02/harry-potter-fantastic-beasts-david-heyman/ |archive-date=2018-06-18  }}</ref><ref name="FBProds" />。

2015年6月，[[艾迪·烈柏尼|艾迪·烈柏尼]]獲選為飾演男主角[[紐特·斯卡曼德|紐特·斯卡曼德]]，魔法世界的傑出魔法動物學家<ref name=RedmayneCast />。其他演員包括：飾演蒂娜·金坦的[[凱薩琳·華特斯頓|嘉芙蓮·禾達史東]]、[[艾莉森·蘇朵|艾歷遜·蘇度]]飾演奎妮·金坦、[[丹·富勒|丹·方格]]飾演雅各·科沃斯基、[[埃兹拉·米勒|埃兹拉·米勒]]]飾演魁登斯·巴波，以及[[哥連·費路|哥連·費路]]飾演波西瓦·葛雷夫<ref name="FBCast">{{cite press release|title=Filming Gets Underway on 'Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them' |date=17 August 2015 |publisher=[[Warner_Bros._Pictures|Warner Bros. Pictures]] |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150817005158/en/Filming-Underway-%E2%80%9CFantastic-Beasts-Find-Them%E2%80%9D |agency=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]] |first=Paulette |last=Osorio |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007023302/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150817005158/en/Filming-Underway-%E2%80%9CFantastic-Beasts-Find-Them%E2%80%9D |archive-date=7 October 2016 }}</ref>。[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2015年8月17日於利維斯登的華納兄弟工作室開始<ref name="Aug2015Deadline">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2015/08/david-yates-fantastic-beasts-filming-under-way-1201500147/ |title=David Yates-Helmed 'Fantastic Beast' Filming Starts Up |date=2015-08-17 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2015-08-17 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150818121532/https://deadline.com/2015/08/david-yates-fantastic-beasts-filming-under-way-1201500147/ |archive-date=2015-08-18 }}</ref>，兩個月後，製作移師到利物浦的[[聖佐治大廳|聖佐治大廳]]。那裡變成了1920年代的紐約市<ref name="FBLiverpool">{{cite news|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/news/showbiz-news/liverpool-harry-potter-prequel-snow-10298308 |title=Fake snow on Harry Potter prequelset as Liverpool filming makes progress |date=2015-10-20 |work=[[Liverpool_Echo|Liverpool Echo]] |last=Miles |first=Tina |access-date=2015-10-21 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022083223/http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/news/showbiz-news/liverpool-harry-potter-prequel-snow-10298308 |archive-date=2015-10-22 }}</ref>。《[[怪獸與牠們的產地_(電影)|怪獸與牠們的產地]]》於2016年11月18日在全球發行<ref name="FBRelease">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/harry-potter-spinoff-fantastic-beasts-to-hit-theaters-nov-18-2016-1201179553/ |title=Harry Potter Spinoff 'Fantastic Beasts' to Hit Theaters Nov. 18, 2016 |date=2014-05-13 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |access-date=2014-05-19 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518091701/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/harry-potter-spinoff-fantastic-beasts-to-hit-theaters-nov-18-2016-1201179553/ |archive-date=2014-05-18 }}</ref>。

=== 怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行（2018） ===
{{Main|怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行}}
自《怪獸與牠們的產地》的事件發生了幾個月後，[[蓋瑞·葛林戴華德|蓋勒·葛林戴華德]]從監獄逃脫了，並開始為其事業聚集追隨者—將巫師提升到所有非魔法生物之上。鄧不利多必須向他從前的學生紐特·斯卡曼德尋求協助才能阻止葛林戴華德<ref name="FB2FilmingBegin">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/07/fantastic-beasts-sequel-plot-details-cast-shooting-start-harry-potter-jk-rowling-warner-bros-1202123376/ |title='Fantastic Beasts' Sequel Reveals Plot Details, Adds Cast As Shooting Starts |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2017-07-03 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2017-07-03 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704211638/http://deadline.com/2017/07/fantastic-beasts-sequel-plot-details-cast-shooting-start-harry-potter-jk-rowling-warner-bros-1202123376/ |archive-date=2017-07-04 }}</ref>。這部電影於2014年3月宣布作為該系列的第二部作品<ref name="FBTrilogy">{{cite news|title=Warner's C.E.O. Is Bullish on the Big Screen |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/business/media/warners-ceo-is-bullish-on-the-big-screen.html |date=2014-03-29 |access-date=2014-03-29 |first=Brooks |last=Barnes |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329221855/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/business/media/warners-ceo-is-bullish-on-the-big-screen.html |archive-date=2014-03-29 }}</ref>。2016年10月，據透露葉慈與羅琳將回歸導演、編劇和聯合製片人的崗位，而烈柏尼將會回歸到電影系列中飾演主角斯卡曼德的角色<ref name="FBFiveFilms">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-five-movies-1201888226/ |title='Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them' to Be Five-Film Franchise |date=2016-10-13 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |last2=Khatchatourian |first2=Maane |last1=McNary |first1=Dave |access-date=2016-11-02 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029012408/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-five-movies-1201888226/ |archive-date=2016-10-29 }}</ref>。2016年11月，電影公司確定[[尊尼·特普|尊尼·特普]]從第一部電影開始飾演葛林戴華德的角色，他將會於續集中擔任主演<ref name="Depp" />。同月晚些時候，電影公司還宣布阿不思·鄧不利多將會於未來的階段中出現，儘管經已有年輕的演員出現於前傳電影系列中<ref name="FBDumbledore">{{cite web|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/784453-johnny-depp-is-grindelwald |title=Johnny Depp is Grindelwald and More on Fantastic Beasts |date=2016-11-08 |publisher=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109153408/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/784453-johnny-depp-is-grindelwald |archive-date=2016-11-09 }}</ref>。2017年4月，電影公司確認[[祖迪·羅|祖迪·羅]]獲選為飾演鄧不利多<ref name="Law" />。這部電影於紐約市、英國和巴黎取景<ref name="FB2Location">{{cite web|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/1587480/fantastic-beasts-2-wont-be-set-entirely-in-paris |title=Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them 2 takes place in Paris |last=Wood |first=Matt |date=2016-11-19 |publisher=Cinema Blend |access-date=2016-11-19 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120130632/http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1587480/fantastic-beasts-2-wont-be-set-entirely-in-paris |archive-date=2016-11-20 }}</ref>。主體攝影於2017年7月3日在利維斯登的華納兄弟工作室開始<ref name="FB2FilmingBegin">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/07/fantastic-beasts-sequel-plot-details-cast-shooting-start-harry-potter-jk-rowling-warner-bros-1202123376/ |title='Fantastic Beasts' Sequel Reveals Plot Details, Adds Cast As Shooting Starts |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |date=2017-07-03 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2017-07-03 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170704211638/http://deadline.com/2017/07/fantastic-beasts-sequel-plot-details-cast-shooting-start-harry-potter-jk-rowling-warner-bros-1202123376/ |archive-date=2017-07-04 }}</ref>，並於2017年12月20日結束<ref name="FB2FilmingEnd">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/fantastic-beasts-2-filming-wraps-video/ |title='Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald' Wraps Filming |last=Chitwood |first=Adam |date=2017-12-20 |website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] |access-date=2017-12-20 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171220203511/http://collider.com/fantastic-beasts-2-filming-wraps-video/ |archive-date=2017-12-20  }}</ref>。《[[怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行|怪獸與葛林戴華德之罪]]》於2018年11月16日發行<ref name="FB2Release">{{cite news|last1=Barraclough |first1=Leo |title='Fantastic Beasts' Sequel in the Works With J.K. Rowling and David Yates, Release Date Set |url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/second-fantastic-beasts-movie-release-set-1201829550/ |access-date=2016-11-02 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2016-08-03 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161105182836/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/second-fantastic-beasts-movie-release-set-1201829550/ |archive-date=2016-11-05 }}</ref>。

=== 怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密（2022） ===
{{Main|怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密}}
在《怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行》的事件發生了幾年後，這次故事的部分發生分別於[[巴西|巴西]][[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]和[[德國|德國]]的[[柏林|柏林]]，並導致魔法世界捲入[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]<ref>{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=46&v=Vjplxx2JzjI&feature=emb_title |title=Dan Fogler Teases Hagrid's Appearance In Fantastic Beasts 3 🦉 {{!}} The Movie Dweeb |last=Fogler |first=Dan |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016232155/https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=46&v=Vjplxx2JzjI&feature=emb_title |archive-date=16 October 2020 |url-status=live |publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Alex |first=Thomas |date=7 February 2019 |title=Exclusive Interview: Dan Fogler on the return of The Walking Dead, Brooklyn Gladiator and Fantastic Beasts 3 |url=https://www.heyuguys.com/dan-fogler-interview-the-walking-dead-fantastic-beasts-3/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930200431/https://www.heyuguys.com/dan-fogler-interview-the-walking-dead-fantastic-beasts-3/ |archive-date=30 September 2020 |access-date=29 September 2020 |website=HeyUGuys}}</ref>。

該系列的第三輯電影將會看到主角紐特·斯卡曼德和他的同伴回到巫師世界進行另一次冒險之旅，以試圖擊敗瘋狂的[[蓋瑞·葛林戴華德|蓋勒·葛林戴華德]]。這部電影原訂於2020年11月20日上映，但其發行時間被改編自[[法蘭克·赫伯特|法蘭克·赫伯特]]小說的新電影<ref name="Aug2016Variety" /><ref name="FB3Release">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2014/10/kevin-tsujihara-time-warner-investor-day-warner-bros-ceo-presentation-851823/|title=Warner Bros' Kevin Tsujihara Outlines Major Film & TV Push Amid Cost Cuts: Time Warner Investor Day|last=Lieberman|first=David|date=15 October 2014|access-date=9 November 2016|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6ltlRr4t0?url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/kevin-tsujihara-time-warner-investor-day-warner-bros-ceo-presentation-851823/|archive-date=9 November 2016|url-status=live|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]}}</ref>《[[沙丘_(2021年電影)|沙丘瀚戰]]》取代<ref>{{cite web|first=Sarah|last=Whitten|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2019/02/19/dune-takes-2020-release-date-from-fantastic-beasts-3.html|title='Dune' takes 2020 release date from 'Fantastic Beasts 3,' signaling trouble for the 'Harry Potter' film|date=19 February 2019|publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|access-date=12 August 2019|archive-date=2022-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220425164610/https://www.cnbc.com/2019/02/19/dune-takes-2020-release-date-from-fantastic-beasts-3.html}}</ref>。該電影原定於2019年7月開始拍攝，但製作被推遲至2019年底，以便有更多時間完善劇本並規劃該系列的未來發展<ref>{{cite web|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/fantastic-beasts-3-pushes-production-start-to-late-fall-1202537147/|title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Pushes Production Start To Late Fall|date=18 January 2019|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=18 January 2019|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119020556/https://deadline.com/2019/01/fantastic-beasts-3-pushes-production-start-to-late-fall-1202537147/}}</ref>。

2018年，[[J.K.羅琳|J.K.羅琳]]於在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上承諾第三輯電影將會回答前兩輯電影中尚未解決的疑問。2019年10月，丹·福格勒聲稱第三部電影的主要攝影將於2020年2月開始<ref>{{cite web|first=Christopher|last=Marc|url=https://hnentertainment.co/dan-fogler-says-fantastic-beasts-3-begins-filming-in-february/|title=Dan Fogler Says 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Begins Filming In February|date=20 October 2019|website=HNEntertainment|access-date=22 October 2019|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022153755/https://hnentertainment.co/dan-fogler-says-fantastic-beasts-3-begins-filming-in-february/}}</ref>。2019年11月，電影公司宣布J. K. 羅琳與[[史提夫·克羅夫斯|史提夫·克羅夫斯]]共同擔任編劇，後者於前兩輯電影中缺席後回到編劇的崗位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wizardingworld.com/news/the-third-fantastic-beasts-film-confirms-new-details-including-cast-members-and-location|title=The third Fantastic Beasts film confirms new details including cast members and location|date=4 November 2019|website=WizardingWorld|access-date=8 November 2019|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200919051402/https://www.wizardingworld.com/news/the-third-fantastic-beasts-film-confirms-new-details-including-cast-members-and-location}}</ref>。第三輯電影的背景設定於1930年代，並以[[巴西|巴西]]的[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]為主要地點<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-five-movies-1201888226/|title='Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them' to Be Five-Film Franchise|last1=Khatchatourian|first1=Maane|last2=McNary|first2=Dave|work=Variety|date=13 October 2016|access-date=9 November 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161029012408/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-five-movies-1201888226/|archive-date=29 October 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>。

2020年3月16日，也就是電影開首拍攝的當天，[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]促使華納兄弟推遲製作其第三部《怪獸系列》電影<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://variety.com/2020/film/news/fantastic-beasts-3-production-postponed-coronavirus-1203535480/|title = 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Production Postponed Due to Coronavirus Pandemic|date = 16 March 2020|access-date = 2021-12-07|archive-date = 2020-08-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200813222117/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/fantastic-beasts-3-production-postponed-coronavirus-1203535480/}}</ref>。2020年8月20日，拍攝確認於9月份展開<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://movieweb.com/fantastic-beasts-3-fall-production/|title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Expected to Resume Filming Sometime in September|date=20 August 2020|website=Movieweb|access-date=2021-12-07|archive-date=2022-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502161835/https://movieweb.com/fantastic-beasts-3-fall-production/}}</ref>。2020年9月20日，[[艾迪·烈柏尼|艾迪·烈柏尼]]確認拍攝正在進行兩星期，期間正採取了安全預防措施，以確保演員及工作人員免受COVID-19的侵害<ref>{{Cite web|last=Webb|first=Katherine|date=20 September 2020|title=Eddie Redmayne Confirms Fantastic Beasts 3 Filming Has Resumed And Describes The 'New Normal' On Set|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923013053/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set|archive-date=23 September 2020|access-date=23 September 2020|website=CinemaBlend}}</ref>。[[尊尼·特普|尊尼·特普]]因在英國的誹謗訴訟案敗訴的結果後，他於2020年11月6日宣布應華納兄弟工作室的要求下離開該電影的崗位<ref>{{Cite web|last=Reichert|first=Corinne|title=Johnny Depp leaves Fantastic Beasts films on Warner Bros' request|url=https://www.cnet.com/news/johnny-depp-leaves-fantastic-beasts-films-on-warner-bros-request/|access-date=6 November 2020|publisher=CNET|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505190748/https://www.cnet.com/news/johnny-depp-leaves-fantastic-beasts-films-on-warner-bros-request/}}</ref>。2020年11月25日，華納兄弟宣布[[麥斯·米基辛|麥斯·米基辛]]將取代特普擔任葛林戴華德一角<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last1=Sharf|first1=Zack|date=25 November 2020|title=Mads Mikkelsen Replacing Johnny Depp as Grindelwald in 'Fantastic Beasts 3'|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/mads-mikkelsen-replace-johnny-depp-fantastic-beasts-3-1234598075/|access-date=25 November 2020|website=IndieWire|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124103414/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/11/mads-mikkelsen-replace-johnny-depp-fantastic-beasts-3-1234598075/}}</ref>。2021年2月3日，在一名製作人員的COVID-19檢測結果呈陽性後，在英國的拍攝被迫關閉<ref>{{Cite web|last=Grater|first=Tom|date=4 February 2021|title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Pauses UK Production After Positive Covid Test|url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/fantastic-beasts-3-pauses-uk-production-positive-covid-test-1234687188/|access-date=4 February 2021|website=Deadline|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205083237/https://deadline.com/2021/02/fantastic-beasts-3-pauses-uk-production-positive-covid-test-1234687188/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=4 February 2021|title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Stops Shoot After Positive COVID Test|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fantastic-beasts-3-suspends-filming-positive-covid-test|access-date=4 February 2021|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|archive-date=4 February 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204134410/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fantastic-beasts-3-suspends-filming-positive-covid-test|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Ramachandran|first=Naman|date=4 February 2021|title=Warner Bros. Suspends 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Shoot After Crew Member Tests Positive For COVID-19|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/global/fantastic-beasts-3-suspended-covid-1234900398/|access-date=4 February 2021|website=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=4 February 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204101258/https://variety.com/2021/film/global/fantastic-beasts-3-suspended-covid-1234900398/|url-status=live}}</ref>。作曲家[[詹姆斯·紐頓·霍華|占士·紐頓·侯活]]在該月稍後時候證實了製作經已結束拍攝<ref>{{Cite web |last=Grober |first=Matt |date=26 February 2021 |title=Composer James Newton Howard on Penning 'News of the World's "Broken" Western Score & Returning to Disney Animation with 'Raya and the Last Dragon |url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/news-of-the-world-composer-james-newton-howard-universal-pictures-interview-news-1234699898/ |website=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2021-12-02 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305023908/https://deadline.com/2021/02/news-of-the-world-composer-james-newton-howard-universal-pictures-interview-news-1234699898/ }}</ref>。

