{{As of|2018}}，首十齣魔法世界電影的全球票房總收入超過$92億美元，使其成為[[全球最高電影票房收入列表|有史以來最高票房電影系列的第三位]]，僅次於《[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]》及《[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]》系列電影。整個系列的所有十部電影都在票房上取得商業上的成功，當中大部分電影的票房收入都超過了$7.9億美元。除了《阿茲卡班的逃犯》與《怪獸與牠們的產地》之外，其他所有電影都曾經一度躋身[[全球最高電影票房收入列表|有史以來最高票房的十部電影]]。《哈利波特電影》是基於單一屬性的最高票房系列，票房收入超過$77億美元<ref name="AllTimeDomesticBOM" /><ref name="HPTotalBOM" />；《哈利波特》還創造了至少$35億美元的家庭影視收入，來自消費者於電影上的總支出超過$110億美元<ref name="TheNumbersHP">{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=6406 |title=Analysis: Harry Potter and the Big Pile of Money |last=Nash |first=Bruce |date=21 July 2011 |publisher=Nash Information Services, LLC |work=[[The_Numbers_(website)|The Numbers]] |access-date=7 September 2013 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929030005/http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=6406 |archive-date=29 September 2013 }}</ref>。根據通貨膨脹進行調整後，《哈利波特》系列的每部電影的平均票房也超過$10億美元<ref name="HPSeriesAverage">{{Cite news|url=https://www.economist.com/blogs/dailychart/2011/07/film-franchises |title=Pottering on, and on |date=11 July 2011 |work=[[The_Economist|The Economist]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303193154/https://www.economist.com/blogs/dailychart/2011/07/film-franchises |archive-date=3 March 2017 |url-status=dead |author=The Economist online |access-date=4 January 2012 }}</ref>。

《哈利波特：死神的聖物Ⅱ》的票房收入超過了$13億美元，成為了有史以來票房收入第三高的電影、魔法世界系列中最高票房的電影，以及[[2011年電影|2011年票房最高的電影]]<ref name="BOM2001highest">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2001&p=.htm |title=2001 Worldwide Grosses |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=14 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702054334/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2001&p=.htm |archive-date=2 July 2017 }}</ref>。在美國和加拿大，它創造了單日和周末開畫記錄，分別為$91,071,119美元和$169,189,427美元<ref name="DH2OpeningDay">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3210&p=.htm |title=Friday Report: ''Harry Potter'' Conjures Opening Day Record |last=Gray |first=Brandon |date=16 July 2011 |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=18 July 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719183118/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3210&p=.htm |archive-date=19 July 2011 }}</ref><ref name="DH2OpeningWeekend">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-final-harry-212331 |title=Box Office Report: ''Harry Potter'' Grosses All-Time Domestic Best of $168.6 Million |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |date=17 July 2011 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=18 July 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717224843/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-final-harry-212331 |archive-date=17 July 2011 }}</ref>。此外，這部電影以$483,189,427美元的票房收入創下了全球首映週末的紀錄<ref name="DH2WorldwideDebut">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-harry-potter-212332 |title=Box Office Report: ''Harry Potter'' Nabs a Record-Breaking $476 Mil in Worldwide Debut |last=McClintock |first=Pamela |date=17 July 2011 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=19 July 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719033509/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-harry-potter-212332 |archive-date=19 July 2011 }}</ref><ref name="TheNumbersDH2">{{cite web|url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2011/HPOT8.php |title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2 |year=2011 |publisher=The Numbers |access-date=3 November 2012 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018071300/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2011/HPOT8.php |archive-date=18 October 2012 }}</ref>。《神秘的魔法石》和《火盃的考驗》分別也是票房最高的[[2001年電影|2001年電影]]及[[2005年電影|2005年電影]]<ref name="BOM2001highest" /><ref name="BOM2005highest">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2005&p=.htm |title=2005 Worldwide Grosses |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=14 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702053807/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2005&p=.htm |archive-date=2 July 2017 }}</ref>；而《消失的密室》、《阿茲卡班的逃犯》、《鳳凰會的密令》及《混血王子的背叛》分別是票房最高第二位的[[2002年電影|2002年電影]]、[[2004年電影|2004年電影]]、[[2007年電影|2007年電影]]及[[2009年電影|2009年電影]]<ref name="BOM2002highest">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2002&p=.htm |title=2002 Worldwide Grosses |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=14 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170624214712/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2002&p=.htm |archive-date=24 June 2017 }}</ref><ref name="BOM2004highest">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2004&p=.htm |title=2004 Worldwide Grosses |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=14 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707041921/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2004&p=.htm |archive-date=7 July 2017 }}</ref><ref name="BOM2007highest">{{cite web|url=https://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2007&p=.htm |title=2007 Worldwide Grosses |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=14 July 201