=== 評價 ===
這個系列的所有電影於商業上都取得了成功，當中大多數於評價上都取得成功，使該系列的特許經營權成為類似於《[[占士邦|占士邦]]》、《[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]》、《[[夺宝奇兵|奪寶奇兵]]》、《[[魔戒電影三部曲|魔戒]]》、《[[魔盜王系列電影|魔盜王]]》、《[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]》及《[[DC擴展宇宙|DC擴展宇宙]]》等熱賣的電影系列。隨著該系列每部電影的上映，觀眾和影評人都注意到《哈利波特》系列的敘事方式逐漸變得更複雜、視覺上逐漸更趨[[黑暗奇幻|黑暗]]和更趨成熟<ref name="ColumbusDark">{{cite news|url=http://live.wsj.com/video/harry-potter-films-get-darker-and-darker/B5548BF1-3398-4597-9D4D-D5DD715DC6A3.html#!B5548BF1-3398-4597-9D4D-D5DD715DC6A3 |title=Harry Potter Films Get Darker and Darker |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |date=18 November 2010 |access-date=9 September 2012 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622184744/http://live.wsj.com/video/harry-potter-films-get-darker-and-darker/B5548BF1-3398-4597-9D4D-D5DD715DC6A3.html |archive-date=22 June 2012 }}</ref><ref name="TimeDarker">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1910978,00.html |title=Harry Potter: Darker, Richer and All Grown Up |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=15 July 2009 |access-date=9 September 2012 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010145917/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1910978%2C00.html |archive-date=10 October 2012 }}</ref><ref name="ReutersDark">{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-reviews-film-harrypotter-idUSTRE76609Z20110707 |title=Review: "Harry Potter" goes out with magical, and dark, bang |work=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=6 July 2011 |access-date=9 September 2012 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702034723/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/07/07/us-reviews-film-harrypotter-idUSTRE76609Z20110707 |archive-date=2 July 2013 }}</ref><ref name="DarkMoody">{{cite news|url=http://www.sfx.co.uk/2011/12/03/isn%E2%80%99t-it-about-time-you-gave-the-chris-columbus-harry-potter-films-another-chance/ |title=Isn't It About Time You Gave The Chris Columbus Harry Potter Films Another Chance? |work=SFX UK |date=3 December 2011 |access-date=9 Septemb