==== 奧斯卡金像獎 ====
該系列的十部電影中有七部獲得了總共14項[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡獎]]的提名。《怪獸與牠們的產地》獲得[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|2017年]]的[[奧斯卡最佳服裝設計獎|最佳服裝設計獎]]，成為了魔法世界首部獲得奧斯卡獎的電影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/02/27/oscars-2017-fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-wins-first-oscar-for-harry-potter-franchise |title=Oscars 2017: Fantastic Beasts Wins First Academy Award for Harry Potter Franchise |last=Dornbush |first=Jonathon |date=26 February 2017 |website=[[IGN|IGN]] |language=en-US |access-date=27 February 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227023421/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/02/27/oscars-2017-fantastic-beasts-and-where-to-find-them-wins-first-oscar-for-harry-potter-franchise |archive-date=27 February 2017 }}</ref>。在2017年奪獎之前，該系列是奧斯卡獎有史以來最高票房但備受冷落的系列，它獲得12項提名，零獲勝<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/297110/thanks-academy-oscars-make-harry-potter-most-snubbed-franchise-of-all-time |title=Thanks, Academy: Oscars Make Harry Potter Most-Snubbed Franchise of All-Time |last=Ryan |first=Joal |date=27 February 2012 |publisher=[[E!|E!]] |access-date=5 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222120/http://www.eonline.com/news/297110/thanks-academy-oscars-make-harry-potter-most-snubbed-franchise-of-all-time |archive-date=3 March 2016 }}</ref>。

