==== 英國電影學院獎 ====
該系列在《[[英國電影學院獎|英國電影學院獎]]》的[[英國電影和電視藝術學院|年度學院獎]]中共獲得34項提名，贏得三項。在2011年2月舉行的《{{le|第64屆英國電影學院獎頒獎禮|64th British Academy Film Awards}}》上，羅琳、製片人海曼和巴倫以及導演葉斯、紐厄爾和卡隆為紀念哈利波特系列電影而獲得「{{le|邁克爾·巴爾肯英國電影傑出貢獻獎|BAFTA Outstanding British Contribution to Cinema Award}}」以表彰哈利波特系列電影<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12353795 |title=Harry Potter franchise to get Outstanding BAFTA award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=3 February 2011 |access-date=3 February 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204111609/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-12353795 |archive-date=4 February 2011 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/outstanding-british-contribution-to-cinema-the-harry-potter-films,1631,BA.html |title=Outstanding British Contribution to Cinema in 2011 – The Harry Potter films |publisher=[[British_Academy_of_Film_and_Television_Arts|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]] (BAFTA) |date=3 February 2011 |access-date=3 February 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110206001409/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/outstanding-british-contribution-to-cinema-the-harry-potter-films%2C1631%2CBA.html |archive-date=6 February 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>。《哈利波特》系列還獲得了《{{le|BAFTA洛杉磯獎|Britannia Awards}}》，葉慈憑著其四部《哈利波特》電影而獲得「不列顛藝術卓越導演獎」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://losangeles.broadwayworld.com/article/BAFTA-Honors-John-Lasseter-and-David-Yates-1130-20110628 |title=BAFTA Honors John Lasseter and David Yates 11/30 |publisher=[[Broadway_Worldwide|Broadway Worldwide]] (Los Angeles) |date=28 June 2011 |access-date=28 June 2011 |quote=The worldwide success of Mr. Lasseter for Walt Disney and Pixar Animation Studios and Mr. Yates' contribution to the final four parts of the 'Harry Potter' franchise makes them global wizards in their own right, and are delighted to honor these remarkable filmmakers with this year's Britannia Award. |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120084528/http://losangeles.broadwayworld.com/article/BAFTA-Honors-John-Lasseter-and-David-Yates-1130-20110628 |archive-date=20 January 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2011/06/john-lasseter-and-david-yates-set-to-be-honored-by-bafta-los-angeles-.html |title=John Lasseter and David Yates set to be honored by BAFTA Los Angeles |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=28 June 2011 |access-date=28 June 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110703082314/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/awards/2011/06/john-lasseter-and-david-yates-set-to-be-honored-by-bafta-los-angeles-.html |archive-date=3 July 2011 }}</ref>。

