=== 舞台劇獎項 ===
==== 羅蘭士·奧利花獎 ====
{{main|羅蘭士·奧利花獎}}
魔法世界的舞台劇《[[哈利波特：被詛咒的孩子|哈利波特－被詛咒的孩子]]》於2017年的《{{le|羅蘭士·奧利花獎頒獎典禮|2017 Laurence Olivier Awards}}》上獲得了11個獎項提名，追平了《{{le|噴髮明星夢|Hairspray (musical)}}》於{{le|2008年創下的記錄|2008 Laurence Olivier Awards}}，並打破了九項紀錄，包括：{{le|最佳新戲劇|Laurence Olivier Award for Best New Play}}、{{le|最佳導演|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Director}}、{{le|羅蘭士·奧利花獎最佳男主角|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actor|最佳男主角}}（傑米·帕克）、{{le|最佳男配角|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role}}（安東尼·博伊爾）、{{le|最佳女配角|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actress in a Supporting Role}}（諾瑪·杜梅茲維尼）、{{le|最佳服裝設計|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Costume Design}} 、{{le|最佳裝置設計|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Set Design}}、{{le|最佳音效設計|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Sound Design}}，以及{{le|最佳燈光設計|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Lighting Design}}。倫敦的作品還被提名至{{le|最佳戲劇編舞|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Theatre Choreographer}}及{{le|最佳原創音樂或新編曲|Laurence Olivier Award for Best Original Score or New Orchestrations}}<ref name="LOAnoms">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/harry-potter-cursed-child-breaks-olivier-awards-record-11-nominations/ |title='Harry Potter and the Cursed Child' Breaks Olivier Awards Record With 11 Nominations |work=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |last=Geier |first=Thom |date=6 March 2017 |access-date=12 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170505050617/http://www.thewrap.com/harry-potter-cursed-child-breaks-olivier-awards-record-11-nominations/ |archive-date=5 May 2017 }}</ref><ref name="LOAwins">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2017/olivier-awards-2017-harry-potter-and-the-cursed-child-wins-record-nine-prizes/ |title=Olivier Awards 2017: Harry Potter and the Cursed Child wins record nine prizes |work=[[The_Stage|The Stage]] |last=Bano |first=Tim |date=9 April 2017 |access-date=12 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415040142/https://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2017/olivier-awards-2017-harry-potter-and-the-cursed-child-wins-record-nine-prizes/ |archive-date=15 April 2017 }}</ref>。

