{{main|東尼獎}}
舞台劇《[[哈利波特：被詛咒的孩子|哈利波特－被詛咒的孩子]]》於2018年的《{{le|第72屆東尼獎頒獎典禮|72nd Tony Awards}}》上勝出六個獎項，包括：{{le|最佳戲劇|Tony Award for Best Play}}、{{le|最佳場景設計|Tony Award for Best Scenic Design in a Play}}、{{le|最佳戲劇服裝設計|Tony Award for Best Costume Design in a Play}}、{{le|最佳燈光設計|Tony Award for Best Lighting Design in a Play}}、{{le|最佳音效設計|Tony Award for Best Sound Design}}及{{le|最佳戲劇導演獎|Tony Award for Best Direction of a Play}}。該舞台劇還獲得{{le|東尼獎最佳男主角|Tony Award for Best Actor in a Play|最佳男演員}}（帕克）、{{le|東尼獎最佳戲劇男演員|Tony Award for Best Featured Actor in a Play|最佳戲劇男主角}}（博伊爾）、{{le|東尼獎最佳戲劇女演員|Tony Award for Best Featured Actress in a Play|最佳戲劇女主角}}（杜梅茲維尼），以及{{le|東尼獎最佳編舞|Tony Award for Best Choreography|最佳編舞}}<ref name="TonyNoms">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/legit/awards/2018-tony-awards-nominations-list-broadway-1202792611/ |title=Tony Nominations 2018: 'Mean Girls,' 'SpongeBob' Score Big (Complete List) |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |last=Cox |first=Gordon |date=1 May 2018 |access-date=2 May 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180502001406/http://variety.com/2018/legit/awards/2018-tony-awards-nominations-list-broadway-1202792611/ |archive-date=2 May 2018  }}</ref><ref name="TonyWins">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/legit/awards/tony-award-winners-2018-complete-list-1202839347/ |title=Tony Award Winners 2018: The Complete List |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |last=Nyren |first=Erin |date=10 June 2018 |access-date=11 June 2018 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180611043413/https://variety.com/2018/legit/awards/tony-award-winners-2018-complete-list-1202839347/ |archive-date=11 June 2018  }}</ref>。

