2011年6月，羅琳推出了一個名為《[[Pottermore|Pottermore]]》的網站以公布即將開展有關《哈利波特》的項目<ref>{{cite news|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=13858046 |title=J.K. Rowling Has Mysterious New Potter Website |publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=16 June 2011 |access-date=16 June 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110618134045/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=13858046 |archive-date=18 June 2011 }}</ref>，當中所有《哈利波特》未來的項目和所有電子下載的東西都會集中於那裡<ref>{{cite news|title=JK Rowling launches Pottermore Website |first=Anita |last=Singh |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8579560/JK-Rowling-launches-Pottermore-website.html |access-date=4 July 2011 |location=London |date=16 June 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711235447/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8579560/JK-Rowling-launches-Pottermore-website.html |archive-date=11 July 2011 }}</ref>。《Pottermore》網站於2012年4月14日向公眾開放<ref name="waiting">{{cite web|url=http://insider.pottermore.com/2012/03/waiting-for-pottermore.html |title=Waiting for Pottermore? |publisher=[[Pottermore|Pottermore]] |date=8 March 2012 |access-date=9 March 2012 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310102525/http://insider.pottermore.com/2012/03/waiting-for-pottermore.html |archive-date=10 March 2012 }}</ref>，該網站讓用戶進行排序，由他們的魔杖選中並玩各種小遊戲。該網站的主要目的是讓用戶透過瀏覽故事內容來進入羅琳之前尚未透露的內容，當中包含超過18,000字有關於《哈利波特》世界裡的人物、地點與物品的資訊<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/06/23/pottermore-secrets-revealed-j-k-rowlings-new-site-is-e-book-meets-interactive-world |title='Pottermore' Secrets Revealed: J.K. Rowling's New Site is E-Book Meets Interactive World |first=Sonia van |last=Gilder Cooke |date=23 June 2011 |magazine=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |access-date=6 January 2013 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829110641/http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/06/23/pottermore-secrets-revealed-j-k-rowlings-new-site-is-e-book-meets-interactive-world/ |archive-date=29 August 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Pottermore website launched by JK Rowling as 'give-back' to fans |first=Alison |last=Flood |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/jun/23/pottermore-website-jk-rowling-harry-potter |access-date=4 July 2011 |date=23 June 2011 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715090227/http://www.theguardian.com/books/2011/jun/23/pottermore-website-jk-rowling-harry-potter |archive-date=15 July 2014 }}</ref>。2015年9月，該網站推出了一個全新設計的網站，當中包含新聞、特寫和文章，以及羅琳從前未發表的作品，並刪除了一些功能，包括交互式片刻插圖、學院盃和學院分類儀式<ref>{{cite web|title=Pottermore |url=https://www.pottermore.com/news/Welcome-to-the-new-Pottermore |publisher=[[Pottermore|Pottermore]] |access-date=8 October 2015 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926135910/https://www.pottermore.com/news/Welcome-to-the-new-Pottermore |archive-date=26 September 2015 }}</ref>。該網站隨後於2016年1月28日推出了全新設計的學院分類儀式，用戶可以在其中退回他們的舊學院或是重新分類<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/harry-potter-what-hogwarts-house-am-i-in-2016-1 |title=You can finally reclaim your old Hogwarts house and wand on Pottermore — here's how |work=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] |date=28 January 2016 |access-date=4 July 2017 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017202805/http://www.businessinsider.com/harry-potter-what-hogwarts-house-am-i-in-2016-1 |archive-date=17 October 2016 }}</ref>。

